Class FxNodeConnectionWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.Parent
        • javafx.scene.Group
          • cz.zcu.kiv.dfs_simulator.view.content.connection.FxNodeConnectionWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StatePersistable, javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class FxNodeConnectionWrapper
extends javafx.scene.Group
implements StatePersistable
    Graphical wrapper of a connection between two nodes. Wrapper allows only symmetrical connections.

      • FxNodeConnectionWrapper

        public FxNodeConnectionWrapper(FxModelNode source,
                               FxModelNode target,
                               FxNodeLink fxNodeLink,
                               ByteSpeed bandwidth,
                               int latency)
        Graphical connection wrapper between two nodes source and target. Created connection is symmetrical. Wrapper connection is oriented from source to target.
        Parameters:
        source - source node
        target - target node
        fxNodeLink - visible link displayed on layout pane
        bandwidth - connection bandwidth
        latency - connection latency in ms
